492
00:39:16.007 --> 00:39:18.343
Suhaani will not marry Adi.
No matter what.


493
00:39:18.844 --> 00:39:21.346
You think this is happening
because we want it to?


494
00:39:21.972 --> 00:39:25.600
Let it be. This is not the time
for sweets. Let's go.


495
00:39:26.393 --> 00:39:28.270
I'm glad we're under no obligations.

496
00:39:41.283 --> 00:39:44.619
Suhaani, listen! 
What happened?

497
00:39:45.662 --> 00:39:50.625
Whatever had to happen has happened.
Let's finish this right here.


498
00:39:50.959 --> 00:39:52.878
Our parents met, right?
What happened?


499
00:39:53.003 --> 00:39:56.173
Yes, they met.
Like Musharraf met Vajpayee.


500
00:39:56.423 --> 00:39:58.300
It was like reliving the Agra summit.

501
00:39:58.425 --> 00:40:02.262
Look, it's not like
they are getting married.


502
00:40:02.345 --> 00:40:04.181
We have to marry.
It's for us to decide.


503
00:40:04.264 --> 00:40:05.432
What will we decide?

504
00:40:06.641 --> 00:40:09.436
By seeking their permission,
we showed them our respect.


505
00:40:09.519 --> 00:40:11.855
The respect we got from your father
is more than enough.


506
00:40:11.938 --> 00:40:13.064
We don't want anymore.

507
00:40:13.148 --> 00:40:14.858
So, my love means nothing?

508
00:40:15.192 --> 00:40:17.611
How long have you known me?
Twenty weeks?


509
00:40:18.153 --> 00:40:20.030
They have brought me up for 20 years.

510
00:40:20.447 --> 00:40:21.990
I cannot leave them for you.

511
00:40:23.074 --> 00:40:26.036
Suhani, I can leave everything for you.
Everything.


512
00:40:27.329 --> 00:40:29.289
Today, you can leave everything for me.

513
00:40:29.372 --> 00:40:33.084
What is the guarantee that tomorrow
you will not leave me for another girl?


514
00:40:33.168 --> 00:40:34.878
What is this sick logic?

515
00:40:35.128 --> 00:40:36.713
So, I have to be the scapegoat?

516
00:40:36.796 --> 00:40:38.465
Why are you making a mountain
out of a molehill?


517
00:40:39.007 --> 00:40:41.301
You saw me, chased me,
professed your love.


518
00:40:41.384 --> 00:40:44.346
That's all. What if I had said no
in the beginning?


519
00:40:44.429 --> 00:40:46.264
I would have thought of it
as your bad luck.


520
00:40:46.348 --> 00:40:47.307
So, do that now.

521
00:40:50.685 --> 00:40:52.270
You are right, 
I'm sorry, okay?

522
00:40:52.354 --> 00:40:55.065
At least listen to me, Suhani.
Please. Just one minute.


523
00:40:55.315 --> 00:41:00.779
What's the hurry?
Let's give it some time.


524
00:41:00.862 --> 00:41:03.907
Ten days? A week?
Till the 15th?


525
00:41:04.366 --> 00:41:05.742
Think about it. 
If you still feel...

526
00:41:05.825 --> 00:41:08.370
What is going to change in one week?
Just leave it.


527
00:41:10.914 --> 00:41:12.832
Suhani, Listen to me.
Lots can happen in a week.


528
00:41:12.916 --> 00:41:15.085
Give it some time.

529
00:41:15.168 --> 00:41:16.253
Please, Suhaani!

530
00:41:16.336 --> 00:41:18.588
Maybe I'll fall in love with someone else?

531
00:41:19.798 --> 00:41:21.967
You love me, don't you?

532
00:41:29.641 --> 00:41:34.562
Today, 9:50 p.m.
MARINE LINES STATION


533
00:41:47.075 --> 00:41:51.246
-Hello, Dr. Bala!
-Aditya, how are you?


534
00:41:51.371 --> 00:41:52.330
I'm fine, sir.

535
00:41:52.414 --> 00:41:56.418
How is Dr. Suhani?
We never get time to talk to her.


536
00:41:56.835 --> 00:42:00.171
She leaves the hospital by 5:30.

537
00:42:00.422 --> 00:42:02.299
-Is it? I know.

538
00:42:02.674 --> 00:42:05.260
I had asked her to meet me today
before leaving.


539
00:42:05.593 --> 00:42:08.680
I got held up and later she was nowhere
to be seen.


540
00:42:08.930 --> 00:42:10.598
Sir, I'll talk to you later.

541
00:42:11.099 --> 00:42:12.934
-What happened?
-He doesn't know.


542
00:42:15.270 --> 00:42:17.522
She left the hospital at 5.30.

543
00:42:19.065 --> 00:42:22.360
Call Rajeev. She must have gone there.
She's just had a baby.


544
00:42:23.862 --> 00:42:26.740
Hello Rajeev!

545
00:42:26.990 --> 00:42:28.992
Adi, where have you guys been?

546
00:42:29.242 --> 00:42:32.287
You don't call, you don't visit.
Didn't even come to meet the baby.


547
00:42:32.370 --> 00:42:33.580
When are you coming?

548
00:42:33.747 --> 00:42:34.956
In a day or two.

549
00:42:35.040 --> 00:42:37.792
The others haven't called either.
Where have they been?


550
00:42:37.876 --> 00:42:38.710
Okay, bye.

551
00:42:56.728 --> 00:42:59.356
Aditya, this relationship will not work.

552
00:43:00.065 --> 00:43:02.067
Lives don't change in eight or ten days.

553
00:43:02.984 --> 00:43:05.820
I've heard they can change in a second.

554
00:43:06.654 --> 00:43:07.739
Mine didn't.

555
00:43:10.867 --> 00:43:12.369
Did you not miss me?

556
00:43:14.579 --> 00:43:15.955
No, there was no reason to.

557
00:43:17.457 --> 00:43:21.586
There is so much to do.
Chores, studies.


558
00:43:25.715 --> 00:43:28.968
-You want to give it a thought later?
-I already have.


559
00:43:37.185 --> 00:43:40.647
-Ok. Bye!
-Good bye!


560
00:43:41.272 --> 00:43:42.482
Be like this always.

561
