How? Sad?

562
00:43:45.944 --> 00:43:47.028
Smiling.

563
00:44:16.474 --> 00:44:19.310
How long will you evade it?

564
00:44:22.439 --> 00:44:25.150
I mean, how long will you avoid
taking the train?


565
00:44:25.233 --> 00:44:28.069
Even if I forget, you won't let me.

566
00:44:50.216 --> 00:44:54.762
Be careful. It's a computer,
not an old typewriter.


567
00:44:55.013 --> 00:44:58.391
-Like, Billu, even we'll be great.
-Who's Billu?


568
00:44:58.725 --> 00:45:01.060
Good old Bill Gates, who else?

569
00:45:01.519 --> 00:45:06.566
Ok, guys! The first computer!

570
00:45:10.403 --> 00:45:12.614
Hello!

571
00:45:13.072 --> 00:45:15.116
Hi, Jeevan uncle!

572
00:45:15.325 --> 00:45:17.702
