573
00:45:19.037 --> 00:45:20.747
Uncle, it's for you.

574
00:45:24.417 --> 00:45:25.793
What are you doing?

575
00:45:42.644 --> 00:45:45.104
What's the matter?
Has it got disconnected?


576
00:45:50.401 --> 00:45:52.946
Then, why don't you talk?
I am not listening.


577
00:46:15.009 --> 00:46:18.805
-Who are you looking for?
-Do you know where Suhani is?


578
00:46:19.264 --> 00:46:21.683
Didn't you guys break up?

579
00:46:23.017 --> 00:46:25.478
Yes, but do you know where she is?

580
00:46:25.603 --> 00:46:28.690
-I've been looking for her for a few days.
-She's gone.


581
00:46:29.357 --> 00:46:30.817
-Gone?
-She's gone to the US.


582
00:46:32.527 --> 00:46:36.239
-US?
-I'm kidding. Medical Camp in Karwar.


583
00:46:41.494 --> 00:46:43.329
-When is she back?
-In three weeks.


584
00:46:43.413 --> 00:46:44.622
Three weeks?

585
00:46:44.956 --> 00:46:46.457
Too long, isn't it?

586
00:47:10.481 --> 00:47:12.358
What do you need this much money for?

587
00:47:12.525 --> 00:47:13.776
I am going out.

588
00:47:14.027 --> 00:47:16.070
Where? Outside Bombay?

589
00:47:17.989 --> 00:47:19.157
Yes, I'll be back soon.

590
00:47:20.158 --> 00:47:21.659
What if your father finds out?

591
00:47:21.909 --> 00:47:23.202
You take care of it.

592
00:47:25.204 --> 00:47:26.539
Are you going with Suhani?

593
00:47:28.833 --> 00:47:29.876
To find her.

594
00:47:32.920 --> 00:47:37.008
The sky was barren

595
00:47:38.468 --> 00:47:41.346
Everything is barren

596
