I walked many miserable miles

598
00:47:47.518 --> 00:47:53.483
It's all such a waste
It's all a wasteland, so futile


599
00:48:05.036 --> 00:48:08.164
Let me meet my darling

600
00:48:08.247 --> 00:48:11.376
Let me meet, just once

601
00:48:12.001 --> 00:48:16.172
Let me meet, just once

602
