613
00:50:38.147 --> 00:50:41.192
When I went in search of you,
My dear beloved


614
00:50:41.359 --> 00:50:44.946
I walked many miserable miles

615
00:50:51.160 --> 00:50:56.040
Look at the fate that is
Etched on my brow


616
00:51:00.127 --> 00:51:05.007
Whenever I saw footprints
I've bowed my head there


617
00:51:17.728 --> 00:51:20.898
How many times must
I call out to you?


618
00:51:20.982 --> 00:51:26.195
Your name is what
I find everywhere


619
00:51:55.391 --> 00:51:57.059
Why did you take so long to come?

620
00:51:57.602 --> 00:52:01.063
I can't live without you.
Not for a day.


621
00:52:01.355 --> 00:52:02.356
Not even a moment.

622
00:52:03.316 --> 00:52:04.191
I love you.

623
00:52:08.988 --> 00:52:10.406
Will you do anything for me?

624
00:52:11.949 --> 00:52:13.618
Should I jump off a moving train?

625
00:52:16.829 --> 00:52:17.914
Marry me.

626
00:52:23.377 --> 00:52:25.796
We'll marry and stay in our own homes.

627
00:52:26.005 --> 00:52:27.506
We won't tell anyone.

628
00:52:28.925 --> 00:52:30.176
-Not a soul?
-No.


629
00:52:30.509 --> 00:52:32.428
When the time is right, we'll confess.

630
00:52:50.237 --> 00:52:52.073
What happened?
What are you thinking?


631
00:52:52.865 --> 00:52:54.158
I am very scared.

632
00:52:54.241 --> 00:52:56.827
Doesn't matter, get married anyway.

633
00:52:57.078 --> 00:52:58.537
Don't be silly.

634
00:52:58.621 --> 00:52:59.956
I am really scared.

635
00:53:00.039 --> 00:53:02.708
I'll give you one slap
and it will be all right.


636
00:53:03.209 --> 00:53:06.128
Every time I told you
to think ten times before proceeding,


637
00:53:06.379 --> 00:53:08.255
you asked me to shut up.

638
00:53:10.925 --> 00:53:12.134
I'm in a dilemma.

639
00:53:15.888 --> 00:53:18.557
I've thought about this
very seriously.


640
00:53:19.141 --> 00:53:21.686
If I felt it was wrong, I would
never let you do it.


641
00:53:22.144 --> 00:53:25.356
Now come on or you'll miss the bus.
Come on.


642
00:53:30.820 --> 00:53:33.280
How come you're wearing
a sari today?


643
00:53:33.364 --> 00:53:34.448
Isn't she looking pretty?

644
