Of course.

645
00:53:36.200 --> 00:53:40.204
But she suddenly looks like, it's time
for her to get married.


646
00:53:40.371 --> 00:53:42.081
Why don't I get her married, then?

647
00:53:42.873 --> 00:53:43.874
Let's hurry up.

648
00:53:43.958 --> 00:53:46.419
We'll definitely miss the bus.
We'll take an auto.


649
00:53:52.675 --> 00:53:54.510
Where are my princesses going
dressed like this?


650
00:53:54.593 --> 00:53:57.596
-We are getting late.
-I am glad I met you.


651
00:53:57.680 --> 00:53:59.056
God bless you.

652
00:54:02.393 --> 00:54:03.686
I'm late today.

653
00:54:06.689 --> 00:54:08.107
Adi which way are you going?

654
00:54:08.190 --> 00:54:09.442
Why don't you carry on?

655
00:54:10.401 --> 00:54:12.403
Aren't you very late today?

656
00:54:12.486 --> 00:54:13.863
Yes, we were discussing
the Gazdar case.


657
00:54:13.946 --> 00:54:15.364
Where are you going in such a hurry?

658
00:54:15.489 --> 00:54:17.783
Close by to meet a friend.

659
00:54:17.867 --> 00:54:19.952
-Get in, I'll drop you.
-No, it's okay.


660
00:54:20.036 --> 00:54:22.955
Get in, you'll waste money on
a taxi otherwise. Sit down.


661
00:54:25.207 --> 00:54:29.128
You haven't informed their
parents, have you?


662
00:54:29.211 --> 00:54:30.963
No, just a few college friends.

663
00:54:31.756 --> 00:54:35.885
Very good. I am tired of marrying
couples in the court.


664
00:54:35.968 --> 00:54:37.803
We're crossing the court,
let's hurry up.


665
00:54:37.887 --> 00:54:40.222
So, Aditya, what's happening these days?

666
00:54:41.223 --> 00:54:42.308
Nothing at all, dad.

667
00:54:43.309 --> 00:54:45.436
I am aware of everything
that is happening.


668
00:54:46.187 --> 00:54:47.188
What?

669
00:54:47.396 --> 00:54:49.815
You haven't completed your law studies,
and you've started a computer business.


670
00:54:49.899 --> 00:54:51.442
-Oh, you mean that.
-What "oh?"


671
00:54:51.525 --> 00:54:52.693
Where will you get the capital from?

672
00:54:53.277 --> 00:54:56.739
-The Bank is ready to give a loan.
-Really?


673
00:54:57.156 --> 00:55:02.995
-Only, if you sign the guarantee...
-Of course. It's your right.


674
00:55:03.412 --> 00:55:05.915
We have a debt to repay to you.
Isn't it our duty?


675
00:55:06.165 --> 00:55:07.124
Where is the groom?

676
00:55:11.295 --> 00:55:12.338
This is going to be interesting.

677
00:55:15.674 --> 00:55:18.677
Aditya, what are you doing at the temple?

678
00:55:19.678 --> 00:55:23.974
-So, this is a temple?
-You don't believe in God.


679
00:55:24.058 --> 00:55:27.937
So, what are you doing here?
You must have a reason.


680
00:55:28.020 --> 00:55:30.773
What can I do, aunty? You have to
come here to get married.


681
00:55:30.856 --> 00:55:34.777
Oh, shut up! Anyway, God will
do his justice.


682
00:55:35.152 --> 00:55:38.364
Does he do his justice
in English or in Hindi?


683
