First, let me finish my internship
and meanwhile


695
00:58:08.389 --> 00:58:12.434
-you establish your business.
-You are being so boring.


696
00:58:13.185 --> 00:58:16.438
Do you know today is our nuptial night?

697
00:58:19.900 --> 00:58:21.068
Can we meet somewhere?

698
00:58:21.777 --> 00:58:23.487
Right now, I am at Jeevan uncle's stores

699
00:58:24.238 --> 00:58:25.572
asking the rates for rice and lentils.

700
00:58:34.707 --> 00:58:36.000
What good night?

701
00:58:38.544 --> 00:58:40.087
All alone.
It's a lonely night.


702
00:58:55.644 --> 00:58:58.063
-Remove your hand. People are watching.
-So what?


703
00:58:58.147 --> 00:59:00.441
You are my legal wife.
Here's the certificate.


704
00:59:01.191 --> 00:59:05.237
-Why are you carrying this around?
-What can I do?


705
00:59:05.779 --> 00:59:07.531
This is the only substitute I have.

706
00:59:10.743 --> 00:59:12.745
Stop calling me your "wife."
And take off your hand.


707
00:59:13.412 --> 00:59:17.541
-Is she your wife?
-No, she is my life.


708
00:59:18.500 --> 00:59:20.461
Sit properly.
This is a public bus.


709
00:59:24.214 --> 00:59:26.383
-Are you married?
-Yes, since 15 years.


710
00:59:29.595 --> 00:59:31.138
I pity your husband.

711
00:59:31.805 --> 00:59:32.848
Nothing.

712
00:59:38.020 --> 00:59:40.522
Suhani, there is a call for you.

713
00:59:58.207 --> 00:59:59.166
What is it?

714
00:59:59.249 --> 01:00:01.001
-I told you I love you.
-I know.


715
01:00:02.127 --> 01:00:03.962
Then, you should also know that
we both have the same address.


716
01:00:05.047 --> 01:00:10.928
Yet, we are both so far.
Tell me, you love me.


717
01:00:12.971 --> 01:00:14.848
Tell the doctor to check
his patients.


718
01:00:14.973 --> 01:00:18.060
I say, hang up.
Sir, it's an emergency case.


719
01:00:18.977 --> 01:00:21.021
We'll have to keep him
in intensive care.


720
01:00:22.147 --> 01:00:23.482
He sounds a little mad.

721
