01:02:54.258 --> 01:02:58.136
Ever so softly in the raag Marva

738
01:02:59.054 --> 01:03:03.475
May our conversations happen

739
01:03:03.559 --> 01:03:08.230
Let not the day set.
Nor the night fall


740
01:03:08.313 --> 01:03:12.526
Let not the sun set

741
01:03:12.859 --> 01:03:17.197
And if it does, let not the
Morning break


742
01:03:17.364 --> 01:03:21.868
Let the night go on and on

743
01:03:40.721 --> 01:03:45.225
Lying to friends,
In somebody else's name


744
01:03:45.309 --> 01:03:51.064
About you and me.
All through the night


745
01:03:54.693 --> 01:03:59.072
You're away too long.
It's so difficult


746
01:03:59.406 --> 01:04:02.284
To just sign and be contented

747
01:04:08.373 --> 01:04:12.919
When will the separation end?

748
01:04:17.883 --> 01:04:22.721
Come every day to me and
Turn the night into a day


749
01:04:26.725 --> 01:04:30.771
Without you, this wind from the east
seems silly


750
01:04:40.572 --> 01:04:44.451
It rushed into my scarf'

751
01:04:45.160 --> 01:04:49.665
You also come and embrace me
Like this wind, some day


752
01:04:49.748 --> 01:04:53.335
Come and embrace me,
Like this wind


753
01:04:59.049 --> 01:05:03.720
Listen, dear friend

754
01:05:03.804 --> 01:05:09.726
If I can't sleep tomorrow,
Call me to you


755
01:05:12.813 --> 01:05:17.526
Keep my head your lap
And sing me a lullaby


756
01:05:22.197 --> 01:05:28.161
Hug me to you under the sheet
Of the night, on the sly


757
01:05:31.498 --> 01:05:37.462
Where even the moon can't approach.
Behind a cloud


758
01:05:50.934 --> 01:05:53.311
Dina is just like me,
she never keeps quiet.


759
01:05:53.395 --> 01:05:54.563
She talks a lot.

760
01:05:54.688 --> 01:05:57.274
If she starts, you'll cover your ears.

761
01:05:57.858 --> 01:06:00.777
She knows a lot. 
Very knowledgeable.

762
01:06:01.153 --> 01:06:03.071
She goes way too deep,
into the finer details.


763
01:06:03.447 --> 01:06:05.073
Don't go by what she says.

764
01:06:05.365 --> 01:06:09.161
Dina is very simple, very tolerant.

765
01:06:09.327 --> 01:06:12.831
She has taken the responsibility
of the entire household and...


766
01:06:12.914 --> 01:06:15.417
She never complains, isn't it?

767
01:06:16.376 --> 01:06:19.129
In fact, it's the same case
with Raghu.


768
01:06:19.713 --> 01:06:22.424
See, he hasn't even opened
his mouth so far.


769
01:06:23.091 --> 01:06:24.843
Just watching quietly.

770
01:06:25.302 --> 01:06:27.679
Raghu, why don't you say something?

771
01:06:28.930 --> 01:06:31.308
If you say yes, then, we'll proceed.

772
01:06:31.641 --> 01:06:35.937
-We are okay with everything.
-Me too.


773
01:06:37.230 --> 01:06:42.277
-You should ask Dina as well.
-You don't worry about that.


774
01:06:44.196 --> 01:06:47.282
We invited you only after she agreed.

775
01:06:49.034 --> 01:06:54.372
When you give your consent,
we'll get an auspicious date fixed.


776
01:06:55.248 --> 01:06:59.419
You've already told me you
don't care for superstitions.


777
01:07:00.962 --> 01:07:05.342
Can I say something
if you don't mind?


778
01:07:07.010 --> 01:07:11.348
Your younger daughter and my younger son
are both studying medicine.


779
01:07:11.431 --> 01:07:12.474
What's it called?

780
