him now.


782
01:07:22.025 --> 01:07:23.735
and you ask your daughter too.

783
01:07:24.069 --> 01:07:25.862
If everything works out,
then it will be great.


784
01:07:25.946 --> 01:07:28.824
Both brothers and sisters
can live in the same house.


785
01:07:33.870 --> 01:07:36.373
What are you saying, mom?
How can this be?


786
01:07:36.706 --> 01:07:40.085
If it can, what's wrong with it?

787
01:07:40.168 --> 01:07:42.379
It's like a yard sale.
Buy one, get one free.


788
01:07:42.462 --> 01:07:48.009
We are not selling our daughters.
They haven't even asked for a dowry.


789
01:07:48.301 --> 01:07:52.556
The boy is well educated.
This is a stroke of good fortune.


790
01:07:52.639 --> 01:07:55.600
-I don't need this kind of fortune.
-Speak softly.


791
01:07:57.269 --> 01:08:00.105
-Wear this.
-What's wrong in this?


792
01:08:00.188 --> 01:08:03.275
