Mom, I cannot marry.


793
01:08:03.567 --> 01:08:07.487
You'll put Dina's marriage in jeopardy.
Now wear this!


794
01:08:14.035 --> 01:08:16.788
She got worried at the mention
of marriage.


795
01:08:19.499 --> 01:08:21.710
Even I had gotten scared.

796
01:08:22.335 --> 01:08:28.133
If I had known about this,
I never would have come.


797
01:08:28.383 --> 01:08:31.219
But, that's how my father is.

798
01:08:31.595 --> 01:08:34.431
He throws the ball in your court
and you have to catch it.


799
01:08:41.313 --> 01:08:43.690
Are you okay with it?

800
01:08:50.697 --> 01:08:51.907
I am already married.

801
01:09:03.501 --> 01:09:07.422
My parents don't know.
I married secretly in the court.


802
01:09:09.174 --> 01:09:10.425
They don't know anything.

803
01:09:52.425 --> 01:09:55.929
11.30 PM, Marine Lines Station.

804
01:10:28.628 --> 01:10:32.132
Railway Colony, Mumbai.

805
01:10:35.844 --> 01:10:37.012
Is Suhani here?

806
01:10:37.679 --> 01:10:39.389
There is no one by that name here.

807
01:10:41.516 --> 01:10:42.684
Go away from here.

808
01:10:52.485 --> 01:10:53.653
Where is Suhani?

809
01:11:08.626 --> 01:11:11.713
Where is Suhani?

810
01:11:13.381 --> 01:11:16.217
-Where is Dina?
-She's not at home.


811
01:11:22.348 --> 01:11:24.392
You tell me where Suhani is.

812
01:11:24.726 --> 01:11:25.894
What's happened to her?

813
01:11:31.149 --> 01:11:32.192
I don't know.

814
01:11:35.820 --> 01:11:37.906
She left the hospital at 5.

815
01:11:41.910 --> 01:11:45.538
It's 11 now, no sign of her.

816
01:11:48.958 --> 01:11:50.752
I've gone home twice.

817
01:11:52.212 --> 01:11:53.463
There is no news of her.

818
01:11:53.671 --> 01:11:57.008
So, where has she gone?
You must have said something to her.


819
01:12:09.938 --> 01:12:13.525
-22 years. Height 5 feet.
-And 2 inches!


820
01:12:14.359 --> 01:12:19.531
Height 5 feet 2 inches.
Wearing a light brown Sari.


821
01:12:21.032 --> 01:12:25.703
A doctor's coat, hand bag,
stethoscope.


822
01:12:26.371 --> 01:12:28.540
Sir, there is a
hospital ID card as well.

823
01:12:29.582 --> 01:12:31.292
Hospital ID-card.
Yes, just check and call me.


824
01:12:33.169 --> 01:12:34.420
Yeah, find out soon.

825
01:12:36.005 --> 01:12:37.090
Call me immediately.

826
01:13:00.071 --> 01:13:01.698
-Uncle, are you leaving?
-Yes.


827
01:13:01.781 --> 01:13:04.242
-Away from home?
-Yes.


828
01:13:35.273 --> 01:13:36.733
Dina should be crying,

829
01:13:36.941 --> 01:13:38.443
for you've ruined her wedding.

830
01:13:39.235 --> 01:13:40.612
I don't want to marry.

831
01:13:41.237 --> 01:13:42.947
Yes, why would you want to marry?

832
01:13:43.698 --> 01:13:45.408
She is the one
who was in a hurry.

833
01:13:45.909 --> 01:13:49.579
The elder one is still unmarried
and the younger one has no patience.


834
01:13:51.080 --> 01:13:54.834
In six months she'll be pregnant
and on the streets.


835
01:14:01.591 --> 01:14:05.345
Get lost. There is no place for
you in this house.


836
01:14:05.720 --> 01:14:08.097
Be sensitive,
he's leaving the house.


837
01:14:08.306 --> 01:14:12.518
Whose house? When was this his house?
This is my house.


838
01:14:12.894 --> 01:14:15.438
Aditya, don't go.

839
01:14:16.022 --> 01:14:18.524
