Where is the newspaper?

911
01:22:04.699 --> 01:22:07.243
I have been waiting for 15 minutes,

912
01:22:07.326 --> 01:22:08.703
hoping to be the first thing you see
when you wake up.


913
01:22:08.911 --> 01:22:10.454
All you want is the newspaper?

914
01:22:13.541 --> 01:22:16.460
Okay, I've taken a good look at you.
Where's the newspaper?


915
01:22:16.544 --> 01:22:19.547
At night you were making big promises.
What now?


916
01:22:19.714 --> 01:22:23.759
-Really? What was I saying?
-Liar.


917
01:22:24.343 --> 01:22:25.511
You aren't worried about your wife,

918
01:22:25.594 --> 01:22:27.221
but, you want to know
what's happening in Patna.


919
01:22:28.723 --> 01:22:30.975
-Please give me the paper.
-You won't get it.


920
01:22:31.142 --> 01:22:33.394
You can't get your wife
and the news together.


921
01:22:34.270 --> 01:22:36.814
Suhani, where's the paper?

922
01:22:37.773 --> 01:22:40.526
-But, what's happened in Patna?
-Riots have broken out.


923
01:22:47.992 --> 01:22:48.993
Where is the paper?

924
01:22:49.076 --> 01:22:52.788
-Here's your hot news.
-What madness is this?


925
01:22:54.915 --> 01:22:56.751
-Hey kids! What's going on?
-Nothing.


926
01:22:56.834 --> 01:23:00.671
Why are you burning the house?

927
01:23:01.380 --> 01:23:04.675
-But, this is my house
-How's it your own house?


928
01:23:04.759 --> 01:23:08.554
That will happen when you pay the rent.
What did you tell Pushy?


929
01:23:08.637 --> 01:23:10.556
That you'd pay 5 months rent in advance.
Where is it?


930
01:23:10.639 --> 01:23:15.227
-I meant the first of the month.
-That was a long time ago.


931
01:23:15.478 --> 01:23:19.231
-No, I meant the 1st of next month.
-Uncle, why don't you have some tea?


932
01:23:19.315 --> 01:23:21.066
It's getting cold, please drink it.

933
01:23:22.067 --> 01:23:26.906
