I've been waiting here for an hour.

947
01:24:25.548 --> 01:24:27.925
If you were going to take that long,
you should've left the keys with someone.


948
01:24:28.092 --> 01:24:29.718
With whom? Pushy Aunty?

949
01:24:29.802 --> 01:24:30.886
And what if she'd asked for the rent?

950
01:24:30.970 --> 01:24:33.097
So, should I just keep sitting
until her Excellency arrives?


951
01:24:33.848 --> 01:24:38.227
Do you think I went for a stroll?
I had gone to shop for our dinner.


952
01:24:38.310 --> 01:24:42.147
But, what's the idea behind
making me sit like a guard?


953
01:24:42.231 --> 01:24:44.441
Why are you making a mountain
of a mole hill?


954
01:24:44.525 --> 01:24:46.902
You used to wait for two hours
at the station before marriage.


955
01:24:46.986 --> 01:24:49.196
We're you working there part-time?
Let's go.


956
01:24:50.990 --> 01:24:53.534
-It was different back then.
-What?


957
01:24:53.951 --> 01:24:55.244
Different how?

958
01:24:55.578 --> 01:24:56.662
Open the door.

959
01:24:56.745 --> 01:24:58.664
-Because we weren't married?
-Yes. I mean, no.


960
01:24:58.747 --> 01:25:00.958
And now that we're married,
you don't care anymore?


961
01:25:01.041 --> 01:25:03.627
-When did I say that?
-But, that's what you implied.


962
01:25:03.836 --> 01:25:05.170
Give me the key.

963
01:25:05.337 --> 01:25:06.714
Don't change the topic.

964
01:25:06.964 --> 01:25:09.133
Why don't you say it clearly
that you don't need me anymore.


965
01:25:09.216 --> 01:25:11.135
Now, why are you splitting hairs?
Give me the keys.


966
01:25:12.636 --> 01:25:13.971
I won't give him any food.

967
01:25:14.054 --> 01:25:18.058
Once he sleeps hungry, he'll realize.

968
01:25:20.394 --> 01:25:23.230
-And remember this incident.
-And even you remember this.


969
01:25:23.314 --> 01:25:24.690
Every time you fight with me,

970
01:25:24.773 --> 01:25:26.901
I'll keep on making
up with you like this.

971
01:25:26.984 --> 01:25:27.985
Let go of me.

972
01:25:30.321 --> 01:25:31.447
Now now.

973
01:25:31.947 --> 01:25:33.490
That's what you said before
marriage also.


974
01:25:33.574 --> 01:25:35.951
Exactly. Because, unlike you,
I've not changed after marriage.


975
01:25:39.872 --> 01:25:41.040
Now, what is this?

976
01:25:41.582 --> 01:25:45.210
-I'll mark the days we fight.
-Why?


977
01:25:45.544 --> 01:25:48.172
To prove that getting married
is very risky business.


978
01:25:48.339 --> 01:25:52.217
That is true. Considering the way
you fight with me at night


979
01:25:52.509 --> 01:25:55.638
and bite and claw me.
Should I show you the marks?


980
01:25:55.721 --> 01:25:57.848
Do you want to see them?

981
01:26:00.017 --> 01:26:03.520
The mood is pleasant

982
01:26:04.813 --> 01:26:05.731
What's it?

983
01:26:05.814 --> 01:26:07.358
Looking for me?

984
01:26:07.816 --> 01:26:09.193
Where is my mangalsutra?

985
01:26:09.276 --> 01:26:12.029
Forget it, I am alive right here
and ready to be hugged.


986
01:26:12.112 --> 01:26:15.532
You took it off at night
saying it pricks.


987
01:26:19.078 --> 01:26:22.623
I am the symbol of your marriage.
Why don't you hug me?


988
01:26:23.332 --> 01:26:25.584
You prick even more.
Where is my mangalsutra?


989
01:26:26.752 --> 01:26:30.381
Aunty she'll ask for the rent.
Leave me, you shameless!


990
01:26:37.513 --> 01:26:39.473
-How was it last night?
-What?


991
01:26:40.057 --> 01:26:45.354
-Dhansak. Did you not eat it?
-Oh that! That was great.


992
01:26:45.604 --> 01:26:47.106
She cleaned up all of it.

993
01:26:47.690 --> 01:26:49.525
Now, you don't even need
to clean the utensils.


994
01:26:49.817 --> 01:26:54.822
Why don't you go and take the recipe
from Aunty this evening?


995
01:26:57.616 --> 01:27:00.369
What is this mangalsutra
doing here?


996
01:27:00.452 --> 01:27:03.706
-Suhani, this should not be taken off.
-Yes.


997
01:27:03.789 --> 01:27:05.541
I have been searching for this
all morning.


998
01:27:05.624 --> 01:27:07.126
I'm sure you hid it.

999
01:27:07.209 --> 01:27:11.005
Why should I hide it?
I thought I should wear it.


1000
01:27:11.463 --> 01:27:13.716
Sometimes even the man should
look married.


1001
01:27:19.555 --> 01:27:21.140
-How much sugar?
-One spoon.


1002
01:27:31.775 --> 01:27:35.612
Here comes our friend. Wait and see.
He's going to start a fight.


1003
01:27:39.908 --> 01:27:41.035
Wait for a minute.

1004
01:27:43.829 --> 01:27:44.788
-How are you?
-Fine.


1005
01:27:46.790 --> 01:27:48.709
-How are you? Having tea?
-Fine.


1006
01:27:50.669 --> 01:27:51.587
I'll just be back.

1007
01:27:58.135 --> 01:27:59.803
You won't start the fight, right?

1008
01:28:07.227 --> 01:28:09.730
Suhani, where is my project report file?

1009
01:28:10.314 --> 01:28:13.025
Are you listening to me?
Where is my file?


1010
01:28:14.735 --> 01:28:17.905
I've told you so many times
not to move my things around.


1011
01:28:22.326 --> 01:28:23.410
Why are you laughing?

1012
01:28:37.633 --> 01:28:41.887
-Please stop it.
-Suhani, take her out.


1013
01:28:41.970 --> 01:28:44.723
-Please come with me come.
-No, I won't go.


1014
01:28:46.433 --> 01:28:48.644
No, I won't leave.

1015
01:28:51.230 --> 01:28:53.857
If you don't let the doctors work,
what will they do?


1016
01:28:54.942 --> 01:28:57.611
Let them try. They'll try and save
your son.


1017
01:28:57.945 --> 01:29:01.657
He's been here for two days.
Nothing has been done.


1018
01:29:01.990 --> 01:29:03.826
Why don't you say anything, doctor?

1019
01:29:15.295 --> 01:29:17.840
Suhani, what's there to eat?
I am very hungry.


1020
01:29:26.974 --> 01:29:29.977
-What happened?
-Let me stay like this.


1021
01:29:32.521 --> 01:29:35.691
-Everyone is looking.
-Let them.


1022
01:29:40.654 --> 01:29:41.864
I am your wife.

1023
01:29:42.698 --> 01:29:44.283
You're embarrassed to hug me?

1024
01:29:47.369 --> 01:29:48.579
Let your reasons be.

1025
01:29:49.037 --> 01:29:51.748
Can't you even ask
me how my day was?

1026
01:29:58.755 --> 01:30:02.426
How would I know what happened
at the hospital?


1027
01:30:02.593 --> 01:30:04.428
I was confused as to why...

1028
01:30:04.511 --> 01:30:08.515
-Don't touch me.
-Why not?


1029
01:30:10.267 --> 01:30:13.312
Forgot how you used to
figure out my mood on the phone?


1030
01:30:13.395 --> 01:30:15.689
"Why are you so restless?"

1031
01:30:16.106 --> 01:30:20.777
You knew if I had fought with mum
the moment you saw me.


1032
01:30:21.653 --> 01:30:25.824
You used to call me twice a day
just to know how I was feeling.


1033
01:30:25.908 --> 01:30:28.577
-Don't you remember?
-I remember.


1034
01:30:29.661 --> 01:30:31.872
In spite of living in the same city
and having a phone,


1035
01:30:32.289 --> 01:30:35.292
you used to send me telegrams
to cheer me up.


1036
01:30:35.375 --> 01:30:36.710
Where did all that vanish?

1037
01:30:38.587 --> 01:30:42.216
I am still ready to do all that.
But, when will you grow up?


1038
01:30:42.466 --> 01:30:46.720
We aren't college students anymore.

1039
01:30:47.179 --> 01:30:49.264
We are responsible for each other.

1040
01:30:51.683 --> 01:30:54.061
Do people stop loving after marriage?

1041
01:31:27.344 --> 01:31:28.720
Don't stare like that.

1042
01:31:30.806 --> 01:31:34.518
Do you think of us and wonder
if we're dead or alive?


1043
01:31:36.019 --> 01:31:37.562
Don't speak like that.

1044
01:31:38.313 --> 01:31:42.276
Not a day goes by
without thinking of you all.


1045
01:31:42.901 --> 01:31:43.944
I had even called.

1046
01:31:44.695 --> 01:31:46.071
You could have come home.

1047
01:31:46.822 --> 01:31:48.031
How could I have?

1048
01:31:49.283 --> 01:31:53.787
Don't you remember what you and dad
said when you threw me out?


1049
01:31:55.747 --> 01:31:58.000
Your father's anger will be the end
of us all.


1050
01:31:58.583 --> 01:32:02.796
-He's in hospital.
-What's happened to dad?


1051
01:32:04.715 --> 01:32:06.133
I am not the doctor.

1052
01:32:06.216 --> 01:32:08.051
We've got a lot
of tests done, but...


1053
01:32:12.889 --> 01:32:14.349
These tests are for jaundice.

1054
01:32:16.059 --> 01:32:18.603
Mom, I want to see dad.

1055
01:32:21.773 --> 01:32:27.279
If you come, he will be pleased.
We came to call you.


1056
01:32:29.865 --> 01:32:32.909
But, don't tell him that we met.

1057
01:32:46.340 --> 01:32:48.508
Adi, Suhani is here.

1058
01:32:48.925 --> 01:32:50.886
Hi. What happened?
How come you didn't go to work?


1059
01:32:54.723 --> 01:32:57.434
Dad is in hospital.
Can we go and meet him?


1060
01:33:01.438 --> 01:33:06.234
Didn't you say that we wouldn't
keep in touch with them?


1061
01:33:08.570 --> 01:33:12.449
-Now, what happened?
-Yes, but he is unwell.


1062
01:33:13.033 --> 01:33:15.911
-He's in the Railway Hospital.
-Who told you?


1063
01:33:16.745 --> 01:33:19.706
He's got jaundice.
He cannot be treated there.


1064
01:33:20.874 --> 01:33:22.000
Who told you all this?

1065
01:33:23.877 --> 01:33:27.464
Mom and Dina.
I met them in the train.


1066
01:33:29.257 --> 01:33:32.719
They know where we live
and where I work.


1067
01:33:35.514 --> 01:33:39.309
But, they didn't think it necessary
to tell me.


1068
01:33:39.559 --> 01:33:42.187
It's not that.
Why do you think like that?


1069
01:33:45.190 --> 01:33:48.610
I still remember my promise,
but you are forgetting yours.


1070
01:33:50.404 --> 01:33:53.615
He spent his entire life savings
to make me a doctor.


1071
01:33:54.866 --> 01:33:56.660
What good is my being a doctor if...

1072
01:33:56.743 --> 01:34:01.206
Dr. Suhani, if your education is
compelling you, then you may go.


1073
01:34:01.832 --> 01:34:04.626
Neither am I a doctor
nor am I compelled in any way.


1074
01:34:05.669 --> 01:34:06.753
Why are you being so indifferent?

1075
01:34:08.046 --> 01:34:10.257
I don't have anyone else
except you and them.


1076
01:34:10.799 --> 01:34:13.343
We are the only ones they have.

1077
01:34:13.510 --> 01:34:17.431
Suhani, I have not forgotten
that slap till today.


1078
01:34:20.934 --> 01:34:22.978
If you want to go, you may.

1079
01:34:53.717 --> 01:34:54.843
How's your father?

1080
01:34:58.805 --> 01:34:59.806
How would I know?

1081
01:35:02.726 --> 01:35:03.852
Didn't you go?

1082
01:35:05.187 --> 01:35:07.272
How could I? I had promised.

1083
01:35:08.565 --> 01:35:12.736
Then, break the promise.
Let's go tomorrow.


1084
01:35:14.362 --> 01:35:15.989
What if he says something again?

1085
01:35:17.199 --> 01:35:20.410
When I've been slapped by him,
how does a little scolding matter?


1086
01:35:21.578 --> 01:35:24.289
Let's go tomorrow.

1087
01:35:30.545 --> 01:35:32.005
Even if he says something,
listen quietly.


1088
01:35:32.672 --> 01:35:34.090
Don't look sad.

1089
01:35:34.174 --> 01:35:37.052
I have worn this especially for you dad.
Don't I look smart?


1090
01:35:37.135 --> 01:35:40.514
Go fast. Something sad has happened.

1091
01:35:40.597 --> 01:35:42.098
-What?
-Go home.


1092
01:36:20.512 --> 01:36:25.225
Don't touch him.
Let his soul rest in peace.


1093
01:36:28.395 --> 01:36:32.941
No child would have
done this to their parents.


1094
01:36:34.651 --> 01:36:38.238
Now, take your husband
and leave our house.


1095
01:36:39.072 --> 01:36:40.323
Mother.

1096
01:37:10.895 --> 01:37:12.480
Daddy.

1097
01:37:44.679 --> 01:37:47.599
All my hopes are now pinned
on the Sintel project.


1098
01:37:49.601 --> 01:37:53.104
If we lose that, then,
we'll have to shut shop.


1099
01:37:55.148 --> 01:37:57.275
You know about the overheads.

1100
01:38:02.489 --> 01:38:05.909
Now, stop it please.
How long will you keep crying?


1101
01:38:07.911 --> 01:38:09.454
It's been so many days.

1102
01:38:09.537 --> 01:38:12.999
What should I do
if I feel like crying?

1103
01:38:15.710 --> 01:38:18.088
Had I not insisted on marrying,
all this would never have happened.


1104
01:38:19.339 --> 01:38:23.760
It was I who had insisted
on marrying secretly.


1105
01:38:24.427 --> 01:38:25.637
I was also impatient.

1106
01:38:25.762 --> 01:38:27.514
If you are repenting it,
why don't you leave me?


1107
01:38:28.848 --> 01:38:30.475
If I can live without my father,

1108
01:38:30.558 --> 01:38:33.269
I can live without you.
Leave me alone.


1109
01:38:47.492 --> 01:38:51.246
-What should I say?
-Read what's written, please.


1110
01:38:51.538 --> 01:38:54.207
-What if I get caught?
-It's just a little acting.


1111
01:38:54.290 --> 01:38:55.542
Come on, now.

1112
01:38:56.042 --> 01:38:57.210
I'll give you one slap.

1113
01:38:57.293 --> 01:39:00.839
-Hello! This is...
-Like a coy woman.


1114
01:39:01.047 --> 01:39:04.300
Dina Sharma.
Do you remember me?


1115
01:39:05.218 --> 01:39:07.721
Mr. Sharma's daughter Dina?

1116
01:39:08.430 --> 01:39:12.350
Yes, Miss Dina! What a surprise!
How are you?


1117
01:39:12.976 --> 01:39:18.523
-I am fine. I wanted to meet you once.
-Me? What for?


1118
01:39:19.232 --> 01:39:23.111
Meet me at 4 o' clock,
at the parking lot near Kala Ghoda.


1119
01:39:23.445 --> 01:39:26.823
Tomorrow.
Don't worry, I won't bite.


1120
01:39:39.794 --> 01:39:41.629
Can you connect me to Dina Sharma?

1121
01:39:49.262 --> 01:39:52.515
Miss Dina. Good morning,
this is Raghunath Pandit.


1122
01:39:53.516 --> 01:39:55.643
Maybe you didn't recognize me.

1123
01:39:56.060 --> 01:39:57.479
I recognize you very well.

1124
01:39:57.729 --> 01:39:58.980
What do you want from me?

1125
01:39:59.230 --> 01:40:00.857
I wanted to meet you.

1126
01:40:01.149 --> 01:40:04.611
Why? Was it not enough to
insult my family?


1127
01:40:04.778 --> 01:40:09.949
That's why I want to make things right.

1128
01:40:10.575 --> 01:40:13.453
If you could meet me for 5 minutes.

1129
01:40:15.747 --> 01:40:17.499
Only for five minutes, please.

1130
01:40:18.625 --> 01:40:23.463
Meet me tomorrow at 4 o clock,
at the parking lot near Kala Ghoda?


1131
01:40:23.713 --> 01:40:25.465
I would be grateful.

1132
01:40:38.895 --> 01:40:40.021
Give me one Mid
-Day.

1133
01:41:00.625 --> 01:41:03.169
-Is that Raghu?
-It sure looks like him.


1134
01:41:04.212 --> 01:41:06.339
We were totally ruined after
that incident.


1135
01:41:06.923 --> 01:41:11.886
Dad passed away soon after.
But, why should it concern you you?


1136
01:41:11.970 --> 01:41:16.015
I am sorry for what has happened.

1137
01:41:17.767 --> 01:41:21.354
But, it's unfair of you
to blame me for all of it.


1138
01:41:21.688 --> 01:41:24.607
If that is your attitude,
why did you want to meet me?


1139
01:41:24.941 --> 01:41:26.234
Why did you call me here?

1140
01:41:27.527 --> 01:41:31.239
Excuse me, but it was you who
called me on the phone.


1141
01:41:31.406 --> 01:41:33.074
Otherwise, why would I have come?

1142
01:41:33.908 --> 01:41:35.076
You called me.

1143
01:41:35.159 --> 01:41:38.371
You think I'm mad to call and ask you
to meet me?


1144
01:41:38.705 --> 01:41:39.998
What do you think I am?

1145
01:41:40.290 --> 01:41:42.750
Looks like they are fighting.

1146
01:41:47.088 --> 01:41:48.464
Here is your coconut water.

1147
01:41:49.257 --> 01:41:50.300
I'm leaving.

1148
01:41:51.926 --> 01:41:56.556
-Did you not call me at the factory?
-Why should I?


1149
01:41:57.181 --> 01:42:00.018
You called me at the Bank.

1150
01:42:00.101 --> 01:42:04.439
I did speak to you.

1151
01:42:05.356 --> 01:42:07.609
But you're the one who asked me
to come here.


1152
01:42:09.027 --> 01:42:10.111
Maybe you are...

1153
01:42:14.365 --> 01:42:15.491
Oh God!

1154
01:42:31.382 --> 01:42:32.675
So, this was your doing.

1155
01:42:33.384 --> 01:42:36.304
What do you think you are?
A matchmaker?


1156
01:42:36.930 --> 01:42:38.890
Do you want to start
a marriage bureau?


1157
01:42:39.641 --> 01:42:41.267
I'm sorry.

1158
01:42:42.185 --> 01:42:43.728
I'm really very sorry.

1159
01:42:45.605 --> 01:42:50.777
Your engagement was broken up
because of us, so I thought...


1160
01:43:01.704 --> 01:43:03.581
It's okay. Your intentions were good.

1161
01:43:06.209 --> 01:43:10.380
But, you didn't do well
especially with Dina.


1162
01:43:29.065 --> 01:43:32.193
It's been ten days
since we spoke to each other.


1163
01:43:32.485 --> 01:43:35.863
It's not unusual after marriage.

1164
01:43:36.614 --> 01:43:40.493
Look at Raj and I.
We don't speak for months.


1165
01:43:41.035 --> 01:43:43.162
All our exchanges are through
the servants.


1166
01:43:44.664 --> 01:43:47.792
I think Adi is
sick and tired of me.

1167
01:43:47.875 --> 01:43:49.419
Don't be stupid.

1168
01:43:50.086 --> 01:43:53.464
Everyone says that if Adi ever flirts
with another girl,


1169
01:43:53.798 --> 01:43:55.133
he'll see you in her.

1170
01:43:56.259 --> 01:43:57.635
Is that any less worrisome?

1171
01:44:08.104 --> 01:44:09.147
How is it?

1172
01:44:10.565 --> 01:44:13.651
Looks like someone is very thirsty.
Why?


1173
01:44:13.735 --> 01:44:15.361
The other day when I was giving
you coconut water,


1174
01:44:15.445 --> 01:44:18.614
you were glaring at me.
Am I a matchmaker?


1175
01:44:18.698 --> 01:44:20.366
I should start a marriage bureau.

1176
01:44:20.450 --> 01:44:22.076
I think after this success,
I should start one.


1177
01:44:22.493 --> 01:44:24.287
And when should we make arrangements
for the wedding band?


1178
01:44:25.288 --> 01:44:27.248
Raghu, will you come on a white horse?

1179
01:44:27.331 --> 01:44:28.583
Or should I get a black train
booked for you?


1180
01:44:28.791 --> 01:44:30.293
His family is coming home
day after tomorrow.


1181
01:44:30.418 --> 01:44:32.378
Once things are finalized,
you go ahead.


1182
01:44:38.342 --> 01:44:39.302
What happened?

1183
01:44:41.220 --> 01:44:44.348
I wish Dad were still alive.

1184
01:44:46.434 --> 01:44:49.395
Now drink this and stop the water works.

1185
01:45:21.511 --> 01:45:25.056
-I have ordered some food.
-What for?


1186
01:45:25.723 --> 01:45:28.267
Damn, sorry. I forgot to tell you.

1187
01:45:28.351 --> 01:45:30.603
My friends didn't have a place
to party,


1188
01:45:30.686 --> 01:45:33.856
-so, I called them here.
-I don't want to party.


1189
01:45:34.107 --> 01:45:35.066
Did you ask me?

1190
01:45:36.359 --> 01:45:40.988
I didn't, but, Anju requested
and I said yes.


1191
01:45:41.823 --> 01:45:44.283
Is Anju going to decide
what happens in my house?


1192
01:45:50.832 --> 01:45:52.959
You should have asked me, right?

1193
01:45:59.715 --> 01:46:01.801
So many people
and so little common sense.


1194
01:46:01.884 --> 01:46:04.220
An open door opens like this
and not like this.


1195
01:46:12.145 --> 01:46:13.271
She'll just be here.

1196
01:46:14.188 --> 01:46:17.275
You were very scared of your parents,
how did they agree?


1197
01:46:17.358 --> 01:46:20.319
-I had to smuggle her out
-You are quite brave.


1198
01:46:20.403 --> 01:46:24.365
This is nothing. One day she took Bhaskar
to meet her parents.


1199
01:46:26.617 --> 01:46:28.619
You are quite an intelligent girl.

1200
01:46:28.703 --> 01:46:31.372
How did you ever get stuck
with this Bhaskar?


1201
01:46:31.789 --> 01:46:34.000
The same way I got stuck with her.

1202
01:46:36.627 --> 01:46:40.089
The minute I looked at her,
my mind started to wander.


1203
01:46:42.049 --> 01:46:43.509
You are a very discouraging friend.

1204
01:46:43.593 --> 01:46:45.219
Get married first,

1205
01:46:45.303 --> 01:46:46.929
then, you'll have to find out
the price of food grains.


1206
01:46:48.806 --> 01:46:50.099
Yes, from Jeevan stores.

1207
01:46:50.308 --> 01:46:53.227
Suhani knows the rates quite well.
Remember?


1208
01:46:54.854 --> 01:46:57.231
Men show their true colors
after marriage.


1209
01:46:59.108 --> 01:47:00.151
How's that?

1210
01:47:00.651 --> 01:47:05.031
Before marriage they are
piling on to you everywhere.


1211
01:47:05.823 --> 01:47:09.285
And after marriage they are
embarrassed to even hold you.


1212
01:47:10.244 --> 01:47:11.495
Does that really happen?

1213
01:47:11.579 --> 01:47:14.081
Yeah, I'm embarrassed at my doing,

1214
01:47:14.415 --> 01:47:17.418
so the easy way out is a mangalsutra
to wear around the neck.


1215
01:47:17.668 --> 01:47:20.004
Before marriage,
her man is special to her.


1216
01:47:21.839 --> 01:47:24.759
After marriage, he becomes part of
the everyday.


1217
01:47:25.801 --> 01:47:28.262
For me, Adi can never be ordinary.

1218
01:47:34.268 --> 01:47:37.980
-I should have married you.
-What had to happen has happened.


1219
01:47:38.064 --> 01:47:39.857
You guys are discouraging me
from getting married,


1220
01:47:40.107 --> 01:47:42.485
but remember tomorrow's
engagement party, right?


1221
01:47:47.949 --> 01:47:50.576
-You're done with me, right?
-What?


1222
01:47:52.578 --> 01:47:53.663
What were you saying?

1223
01:47:55.581 --> 01:47:59.752
Come on Suhani,
you know I was joking.


1224
01:48:00.294 --> 01:48:04.966
It didn't sound like a joke to me.
Have I become stale


1225
01:48:05.633 --> 01:48:07.718
or have you started to like someone else?

1226
01:48:08.135 --> 01:48:09.679
Stop this nonsense.

1227
01:48:12.640 --> 01:48:14.850
You never spoke like this
before marriage.


1228
01:48:17.019 --> 01:48:18.145
I am now.

1229
01:48:28.114 --> 01:48:29.615
Nothing has changed even now.

1230
01:48:29.699 --> 01:48:31.993
If you like someone else
you can go with her.


1231
01:48:40.418 --> 01:48:41.669
Now, where should I find
another destiny?


1232
01:48:42.545 --> 01:48:43.796
You were destined for me.

1233
01:48:44.588 --> 01:48:46.799
And now I have to live with this
all my life.


1234
01:48:52.138 --> 01:48:57.143
This what you do.
Taunt first and then cry.


1235
01:49:03.899 --> 01:49:08.446
Do I trouble you so much?
What is my fault?


1236
01:49:10.948 --> 01:49:15.494
My fault is that I left my parents
for you.


1237
01:49:16.329 --> 01:49:17.496
Then, go back to them.

1238
01:50:07.546 --> 01:50:10.674
A history of atrocities

1239
01:50:10.925 --> 01:50:14.220
And yet, you claim authority

1240
01:50:14.970 --> 01:50:17.181
A history of atrocities

1241
01:50:17.765 --> 01:50:20.476
And yet, you claim authority

1242
01:50:28.317 --> 01:50:31.779
You take us by the hand
And hurt us


1243
01:50:32.113 --> 01:50:37.201
Good Heavens, no!
Good Heavens, no!


1244
01:50:39.203 --> 01:50:41.664
Good Heavens, no!
Good Heavens, no!


1245
01:50:42.164 --> 01:50:45.668
This is not done

1246
01:50:45.876 --> 01:50:49.338
A history of atrocities

1247
01:50:49.422 --> 01:50:52.800
And it's blown out
Of proportions


1248
01:50:52.883 --> 01:50:56.220
The lies in the world
Now threaten my life


1249
01:50:56.595 --> 01:50:58.139
They're the ones who
Inflict atrocities


1250
01:50:58.222 --> 01:50:59.890
And they're the ones who complain

1251
01:50:59.974 --> 01:51:03.310
Good Heavens, no!

1252
01:51:03.853 --> 01:51:06.355
Good Heavens, no!

1253
01:51:10.151 --> 01:51:15.197
This is not done

1254
01:51:38.429 --> 01:51:41.515
Friends

1255
01:51:41.849 --> 01:51:47.771
How am I to spend a lifetime
Misled by illusions?


1256
01:51:48.772 --> 01:51:53.402
If only I could take away
Your illusions


1257
01:51:55.738 --> 01:52:00.618
Take away this affliction
Of love too


1258
01:52:00.951 --> 01:52:05.289
Let that be or else
How will you manage?


1259
01:52:07.833 --> 01:52:12.880
Your attitude, your involvement
Shall lead us on


1260
01:52:15.174 --> 01:52:20.387
Life's a boat sailing
Miles across the sea


1261
01:52:22.431 --> 01:52:28.395
We'll have to drown in it,
There's miles of sea ahead


1262
01:52:29.480 --> 01:52:32.900
A history of atrocities

1263
01:52:32.983 --> 01:52:36.237
And the pot calling
The kettle black


1264
01:52:36.320 --> 01:52:39.573
The lies in the world
Now threaten my life


1265
01:52:39.657 --> 01:52:42.910
They're the ones who inflict atrocities
And they're the ones who complain


1266
01:52:42.993 --> 01:52:48.791
Good Heavens, no!
Good Heavens, no!


1267
01:52:50.209 --> 01:52:52.878
Good Heavens, no!
Good Heavens, no!


1268
01:52:53.587 --> 01:52:58.551
This is not done

1269
01:53:23.284 --> 01:53:25.494
I've been looking for you everywhere!

1270
01:53:26.287 --> 01:53:27.830
Why? Is it something important?

1271
01:53:28.414 --> 01:53:33.711
Yes, it's important,
but now I am suddenly shy.


1272
01:53:40.634 --> 01:53:41.760
You?

1273
01:53:43.887 --> 01:53:47.266
I thought, once things get finalized...

1274
01:53:47.600 --> 01:53:48.976
You were hiding it from me?

1275
01:53:49.059 --> 01:53:52.187
Of course not.
That's why I was looking for you.


1276
01:53:52.354 --> 01:53:54.231
I wanted to tell you in person.

1277
01:53:55.024 --> 01:53:57.943
I even stopped Aditya
from telling you anything.


1278
01:53:58.319 --> 01:54:02.948
Aditya knows about this?

1279
01:54:03.782 --> 01:54:06.035
-He's the one who made this happen.
-Yes.


1280
01:54:09.830 --> 01:54:13.792
-Dina, I've got to meet Aditya.
-Go and meet Aditya.


1281
01:54:14.251 --> 01:54:16.503
-I have to go to Raghu's house.
-To meet your mother-in-law?


1282
01:55:00.255 --> 01:55:04.343
We've got the 90 million project
from Sintel software!


1283
01:55:10.641 --> 01:55:16.605
Through the window in bare feet
The moon will stealthily enter


1284
01:55:18.899 --> 01:55:21.485
O beloved, listen to me

1285
01:55:24.405 --> 01:55:27.074
Hey, what are you watching?
This is no film screening.


1286
01:55:27.241 --> 01:55:29.493
Hey you! Stop there.
Where are you going?


1287
01:55:29.660 --> 01:55:31.328
Sir, I have to go to the station.

1288
01:55:31.412 --> 01:55:32.663
Do I have to
write it down for you?

1289
01:55:32.746 --> 01:55:34.289
Can't you hear me?

1290
01:55:35.332 --> 01:55:37.751
You can't go from here.
There's been an accident.


1291
01:55:40.587 --> 01:55:42.923
-Take a U-turn and go back.
-Okay, sir,


1292
01:55:43.590 --> 01:55:44.675
Go on.

1293
01:56:06.196 --> 01:56:08.115
What are you doing?
Waiting for Suhani?


1294
01:56:08.198 --> 01:56:09.158
Like always.

1295
01:56:09.408 --> 01:56:12.286
If you married me, you wouldn't
have had to do all this.


1296
01:56:12.536 --> 01:56:14.288
If she doesn't come
in the next ten minutes,


1297
01:56:14.371 --> 01:56:15.873
we'll elope and get married
in a temple.


1298
01:56:23.422 --> 01:56:26.049
-Is Suhani there?
-She has left already.


1299
01:56:26.467 --> 01:56:27.551
Okay , one minute.

1300
01:56:27.634 --> 01:56:31.054
-Did she say where she was going?
-No, she left after the shift.


1301
01:56:31.638 --> 01:56:34.099
Are you sure she is not somewhere
in the hospital?


1302
01:56:47.070 --> 01:56:50.824
YASHWANT RAO I.A.S. RESIDENCE

1303
01:57:03.670 --> 01:57:04.713
What happened?

1304
01:57:06.340 --> 01:57:08.300
Who was driving? You?

1305
01:57:10.511 --> 01:57:11.970
What was the need to drive?

1306
01:57:12.346 --> 01:57:13.889
You don't even have a license.

1307
01:57:16.350 --> 01:57:17.476
Are you okay?
Did anyone else get hurt?


1308
01:57:18.310 --> 01:57:20.354
Did anyone?

1309
01:57:22.064 --> 01:57:25.442
-Tell me. Who was it?
-A girl.


1310
01:57:26.819 --> 01:57:29.446
How badly did she get hurt?
Tell me.


1311
01:57:30.280 --> 01:57:31.490
Is she alive?

1312
01:57:34.201 --> 01:57:37.579
I don't know.
I got scared and ran away.


1313
01:57:39.873 --> 01:57:43.919
It's all right. Did anyone
take her to the hospital?


1314
01:57:46.171 --> 01:57:47.714
Where did the accident happen?

1315
01:57:48.632 --> 01:57:50.092
Kennedy Bridge.

1316
01:57:53.262 --> 01:57:55.472
You relax. I'll go and see
what's happening.


1317
01:57:55.556 --> 01:57:58.433
-Don't go.
-You go on inside.


1318
01:58:11.655 --> 01:58:14.908
Has an accident case from Kennedy
Bridge been reported today?


1319
01:58:15.742 --> 01:58:17.286
Yes, a girl has been admitted.

1320
01:58:17.369 --> 01:58:19.580
-Is she your relative?
-What? Yes!


1321
01:58:21.373 --> 01:58:24.501
Inform Dr. Murthy and prepare
the O.T. You come with me.


1322
01:58:27.087 --> 01:58:28.755
Hurry up.

1323
01:58:35.387 --> 01:58:37.514
Doctor Khan, come to
the operation theater.


1324
01:58:43.312 --> 01:58:44.479
Is she the one?

1325
01:58:50.652 --> 01:58:51.737
She is critical.

1326
01:58:51.820 --> 01:58:53.030
She has been hurt on her head.

1327
01:58:53.280 --> 01:58:56.450
Doctors can't operate on her until
someone takes responsibility.


1328
01:58:56.533 --> 01:58:58.118
-Name?
-Yashwant Rao.


1329
01:58:58.243 --> 01:59:01.496
-No, what's her name?
-Savitri.


1330
01:59:01.705 --> 01:59:04.333
-Savitri. Savitri what?
-Savitri Rao.


1331
01:59:05.042 --> 01:59:06.418
How are you related to her?

1332
01:59:07.002 --> 01:59:08.045
Husband.

1333
01:59:08.629 --> 01:59:10.589
Good. Come with me.
Some papers have to be signed.


1334
01:59:17.679 --> 01:59:19.014
Where are you coming from?

1335
01:59:19.097 --> 01:59:20.182
From the North.

1336
01:59:20.265 --> 01:59:21.892
Meaning? Are you coming from Kashmir?

1337
01:59:22.142 --> 01:59:24.519
No sir. North Bombay Society, Juhu.

1338
01:59:25.646 --> 01:59:27.481
-And you?
-He is also...


1339
01:59:27.689 --> 01:59:30.442
-What's your name?
-Aditya.


1340
01:59:30.525 --> 01:59:31.693
Where are you going?

1341
01:59:33.695 --> 01:59:37.074
My wife left home in the morning
and hasn't returned.


1342
01:59:37.532 --> 01:59:39.910
-Have you lodged an FIR?
-Yes.


1343
01:59:40.243 --> 01:59:41.745
-Have you checked the hospitals?
-What?


1344
01:59:41.912 --> 01:59:44.206
A girl met with an accident
not far from here.


1345
01:59:44.790 --> 01:59:45.749
Hospital?

1346
01:59:53.173 --> 01:59:56.051
Yes, I am speaking from the hospital.

1347
01:59:57.177 --> 02:00:00.430
Because of the commotion I could
not report it earlier.


1348
02:00:01.390 --> 02:00:03.350
No, there is no
need to cover it up.

1349
02:00:04.768 --> 02:00:09.773
Let the law take its course.
I wanted what?


1350
02:00:11.441 --> 02:00:16.488
No, her relatives have not
been found yet


1351
02:00:19.241 --> 02:00:21.743
Has an accident case of
a girl been reported?


1352
02:00:21.827 --> 02:00:23.370
-When?
-This evening.


1353
02:00:23.578 --> 02:00:26.164
-What's the name?
-Dr. Suhani. Suhani Sehgal.


1354
02:00:26.415 --> 02:00:28.000
There is no one by this name.

1355
02:00:28.458 --> 02:00:30.711
In an emergency case, they obviously
won't know the name.


1356
02:00:30.794 --> 02:00:33.547
Please check for a 22-23 year-old
married woman.


1357
02:00:33.797 --> 02:00:34.923
Just a minute.

1358
02:00:35.007 --> 02:00:39.094
Mrs. Savitri Rao.
Her husband is on the phone there.


1359
02:00:39.678 --> 02:00:41.179
His wife is in the trauma center.

1360
02:00:43.015 --> 02:00:45.267
-Is there any other?
-No.


1361
02:00:55.485 --> 02:00:56.945
I think we are being too pessimistic.

1362
02:00:58.071 --> 02:00:59.489
Never mind. Let's go home.

1363
02:00:59.865 --> 02:01:01.241
Maybe she has reached home.

1364
02:01:01.491 --> 02:01:03.076
Inform me as soon as you get
some information.


1365
02:01:03.744 --> 02:01:05.328
Yes, I am at Wadia hospital.

1366
02:01:22.012 --> 02:01:25.140
We cannot remove the clot
without a surgery.


1367
02:01:37.944 --> 02:01:40.322
No, you listen to what I'm saying.

1368
02:01:41.531 --> 02:01:44.910
Our area starts from this side
of the bridge.


1369
02:01:44.993 --> 02:01:47.370
If the blast is on that side...

1370
02:01:48.663 --> 02:01:50.624
Can't you see that I am talking
to someone?


1371
02:01:50.749 --> 02:01:51.792
I see that, sir.

1372
02:01:52.209 --> 02:01:53.126
For the past half hour

1373
02:01:53.210 --> 02:01:55.087
you are discussing the sides
of the bridge.


1374
02:01:55.837 --> 02:01:57.464
I'll call you back.

1375
02:02:00.383 --> 02:02:01.468
What is your problem?

1376
02:02:01.885 --> 02:02:04.137
Sir, it's been so long since
I lodged an FIR.


1377
02:02:04.221 --> 02:02:07.432
My wife is missing.
Have you found anything?


1378
02:02:07.516 --> 02:02:09.142
We'll tell you when we find out.
Now, go away.


1379
02:02:09.226 --> 02:02:10.519
Will the news travel to you?

1380
02:02:11.103 --> 02:02:13.980
Sir, at least make an attempt.
Have you inquired?


1381
02:02:14.064 --> 02:02:15.398
You might know who she has
eloped with.


1382
02:02:15.482 --> 02:02:16.608
Why are you wasting my time?

1383
02:02:18.360 --> 02:02:20.320
How dare you assault a cop
inside a police station?


1384
02:02:20.403 --> 02:02:21.530
How dare you talk about my wife?

1385
02:02:21.613 --> 02:02:22.614
Leave me. Let me go

1386
02:02:22.697 --> 02:02:23.782
What if I don't leave it?
What can you do?


1387
02:02:23.865 --> 02:02:24.991
Even you'll be reported missing.

1388
02:02:26.118 --> 02:02:28.036
Leave him!

1389
02:02:29.204 --> 02:02:32.207
Sir, he's the son of Barrister Seghal.

1390
02:02:32.290 --> 02:02:33.917
His wife has been missing
for so many hours.


1391
02:02:45.053 --> 02:02:48.056
I told you I'd take care of everything.
Why did you come here?


1392
02:02:49.474 --> 02:02:51.143
You are taking care of me.

1393
02:02:54.062 --> 02:02:57.232
The surgery is over
but your wife is still unconscious.


1394
02:02:57.357 --> 02:02:58.817
You'll have to wait.

1395
02:02:59.526 --> 02:03:03.280
-I hope there is nothing to fear?
-She's still in coma


1396
02:03:23.425 --> 02:03:24.676
We have located the FIR.

1397
02:03:25.302 --> 02:03:26.636
The girl's husband has lodged it.

1398
02:03:27.554 --> 02:03:28.805
His name is Aditya Sehgal.

1399
02:03:29.764 --> 02:03:30.807
It won't be difficult to trace.

1400
02:03:30.891 --> 02:03:32.392
You don't have to worry now.

1401
02:03:33.435 --> 02:03:34.895
Even he is tracing her frantically.

1402
02:03:37.355 --> 02:03:39.441
You both go home.
I'm here, isn't it?


1403
02:03:40.108 --> 02:03:43.278
No. We'll wait here.

1404
02:03:44.946 --> 02:03:46.573
Once we hand her over to him,

1405
02:03:47.908 --> 02:03:49.284
then, it's up to him.

1406
02:03:52.495 --> 02:03:53.955
What can the poor boy do
in this crisis?


1407
02:03:56.208 --> 02:03:59.669
Don't worry. Savitri didn't do
it deliberately.


1408
02:04:00.295 --> 02:04:01.421
It's an accident.

1409
02:04:03.089 --> 02:04:06.009
Whatever it is.
We'll wait here.


1410
02:04:09.971 --> 02:04:11.514
Okay I'll go and locate him then.

1411
02:04:21.983 --> 02:04:24.903
-Is there a Aditya Sehgal among you?
-Yes. I am.


1412
02:04:25.237 --> 02:04:29.241
Aditya, Did you lodge an FIR
about your missing wife?


1413
02:04:29.324 --> 02:04:31.993
-Yes, have you found anything?
-What was she wearing?


1414
02:04:32.077 --> 02:04:34.871
-A light brown sari.
-Any watch or handbag?


1415
02:04:34.955 --> 02:04:38.041
Yes, A watch, handbag, stethoscope.
I had mentioned everything.


1416
02:04:38.124 --> 02:04:39.251
-Come with me.
-Where?


1417
02:04:39.542 --> 02:04:44.422
To your wife. Come on, sit inside.

1418
02:04:58.770 --> 02:05:00.272
Over there. She is in the ICU.

1419
02:05:20.375 --> 02:05:23.253
Suhani. Open your eyes.

1420
02:05:25.547 --> 02:05:27.966
You would talk throughout the day.

1421
02:05:28.717 --> 02:05:30.093
Now, why don't you speak?

1422
02:05:31.344 --> 02:05:33.680
Say something. 
Open your eyes.

1423
02:05:36.099 --> 02:05:40.687
Are you angry with me?
Please don't be.


1424
02:05:42.022 --> 02:05:46.318
Open your eyes.
Say something, please.


1425
02:06:07.547 --> 02:06:08.715
Let us check.

1426
02:06:42.957 --> 02:06:45.126
That's the man whose car hit Suhani.

1427
02:06:46.127 --> 02:06:48.505
He's signed for the surgery as well.

1428
02:07:11.903 --> 02:07:14.322
How is she?

1429
02:07:20.954 --> 02:07:22.038
You should pray...

1430
02:07:24.499 --> 02:07:25.834
for yourself.

1431
02:07:29.421 --> 02:07:33.591
If anything happens to her,
I won't let you live in peace.


1432
02:07:50.066 --> 02:07:51.484
How did you hit her?

1433
02:07:56.239 --> 02:07:58.700
And why didn't you tell the police?

1434
02:08:05.707 --> 02:08:08.168
You were drinking and driving,
weren't you?


1435
02:08:20.263 --> 02:08:21.556
I won't let you get away.

1436
02:08:31.691 --> 02:08:32.984
It's not his fault.

1437
02:08:38.031 --> 02:08:39.491
Then, whose fault is it?

1438
02:08:42.368 --> 02:08:44.162
The one who is battling
for her life?


1439
02:08:45.330 --> 02:08:46.873
Nothing will happen to her.

1440
02:08:50.168 --> 02:08:53.588
Before it does, 
I will kill myself.

1441
02:09:03.973 --> 02:09:07.519
I hit her. It was my car.

1442
02:09:08.019 --> 02:09:09.646
Why should you be punished for that?

1443
02:09:09.729 --> 02:09:13.399
No harm will befall her.
There is a God above.


1444
02:09:15.068 --> 02:09:17.028
What we could do, we have done.

1445
02:09:35.797 --> 02:09:37.423
You can give us whatever punishment
you want to.


1446
02:09:40.468 --> 02:09:45.098
But, right now even we are praying
for your wife's recovery.


1447
02:11:24.614 --> 02:11:26.532
I know you are listening
to everything.


1448
02:11:29.744 --> 02:11:31.287
You are just pretending.

1449
02:11:33.373 --> 02:11:37.168
To trouble me, to fight with me.

1450
02:11:41.839 --> 02:11:45.802
Come now, get up. Right now.

1451
02:11:50.640 --> 02:11:52.558
Aren't you going to mark
the date on the calendar?


1452
02:11:55.687 --> 02:11:57.355
You didn't come home one day,

1453
02:11:59.107 --> 02:12:01.401
and everything is devastated.

1454
02:12:06.239 --> 02:12:07.865
I've never searched for you this much,

1455
02:12:08.991 --> 02:12:10.576
Not even before we got married.

1456
02:12:17.750 --> 02:12:23.506
The truth is that today
I have understood our relationship.


1457
02:12:28.219 --> 02:12:32.265
For the first time I have understood you.
Found you.


1458
02:12:36.477 --> 02:12:37.645
Now, I can't lose you.

1459
02:12:40.940 --> 02:12:46.362
Till now I was only trying
to find myself.


1460
02:13:01.627 --> 02:13:02.754
Please, love.

1461
02:13:08.050 --> 02:13:09.177
Please come back.

1462
02:14:18.496 --> 02:14:19.539
Were you scared?

1463
02:14:20.957 --> 02:14:21.916
I died.

1464
02:14:26.379 --> 02:14:27.380
What did you think?

1465
02:14:29.090 --> 02:14:30.007
That I'm gone...

1466
02:14:30.132 --> 02:14:31.259
No.

1467
02:14:32.176 --> 02:14:33.511
And you can have fun?

1468
02:14:39.684 --> 02:14:41.519
I love you.

1469
02:14:46.983 --> 02:14:48.526
What can you do for me?

1470
02:14:50.027 --> 02:14:51.654
I love you.

1471
02:14:53.990 --> 02:14:55.366
Can you jump off a moving train?

1472
02:14:58.160 --> 02:14:59.996
Never say that please, not even jokingly.

1473
02:15:21.392 --> 02:15:27.106
Keep laughing, keep laughing!

1474
02:15:27.648 --> 02:15:30.985
May your blushes of modesty
Continue to bloom


1475
02:15:31.444 --> 02:15:35.156
May dusk and dawn continue to meet where
your hair slides across your nape